data.description: Gorgeously renovated 2- unit building with 2 bed/1 bath units on each floor. Perfect for an owner occupant or pure investment property. Both units boast SAMSUNG STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, in unit WASHER/DRYER combo, modern white shaker cabinets, contemporary bathrooms and ebony hardwood floors. The plumbing and electrical system were updated in 2020. There is a parking pad behind the enclosed yard. Current rent below market rate. Tenants pay for their own electric, gas and heating utilities. Tons of extra storage in the basement. Property close to schools, grocery stores and transportation. Home SOLD AS-IS. Don't miss out on this cash flowing building. Schedule your showing TODAY!
